# qmd exclusion list — files and dirs excluded from BM25/vector indexing

# Operational logs and archives (high-noise, low-signal)
wiki/log.md
wiki/log-archive/
wiki/_inbox/edges-archive/

# Stub queues (not synthesis)
wiki/tofile/

# Internal state and tooling
.kb-staging/
raw/.collect-state.json
raw/.ingest-state.json
.kb/extract-state.json
.qmd/

# Session memory buffer
.remember/
